om the ground up to provide an <strong>experience</strong> second to none anywhere in the world.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label="row" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" width_unit="off" custom_width_px="1080px" custom_width_percent="80%" use_custom_gutter="off" gutter_width="3" padding_mobile="off" allow_player_pause="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="on" make_equal="off" column_padding_mobile="on" parallax_1="off" parallax_method_1="on" parallax_2="off" parallax_method_2="on" parallax_3="off" parallax_method_3="on" parallax_4="off" parallax_method_4="on"][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_image admin_label="Image" src="http://localhost/ITico/web/viarama.co.uk/public_html/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/160122-Vive-V1PT5-Duo-Controllers.png" show_in_lightbox="off" url_new_window="off" use_overlay="off" animation="left" sticky="off" align="left" force_fullwidth="off" always_center_on_mobile="on"] [/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_image admin_label="Image" src="http://localhost/ITico/web/viarama.co.uk/public_html/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/160129-Vive-V1PT5-CV1-Ortho.png" show_in_lightbox="off" url_new_window="off" use_overlay="off" animation="left" sticky="off" align="left" force_fullwidth="off" always_center_on_mobile="on"] [/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_image admin_label="Image" src="http://localhost/ITico/web/viarama.co.uk/public_html/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/160122-Vive-V1PT5-v56-Perspective.png" show_in_lightbox="off" url_new_window="off" use_overlay="off" animation="left" sticky="off" align="left" force_fullwidth="off" always_center_on_mobile="on"] [/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label="row" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" width_unit="off" custom_width_px="1080px" custom_width_percent="80%" use_custom_gutter="off" gutter_width="3" padding_mobile="off" allow_player_pause="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="on" make_equal="off" column_padding_mobile="on" parallax_1="off" parallax_method_1="on" parallax_2="off" parallax_method_2="on" parallax_3="off" parallax_method_3="on" parallax_4="off" parallax_method_4="on"][et_pb_column type="2_3"][et_pb_text admin_label="Text" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Intuitive</strong> to use. <strong>Comfortable</strong> to wear. <strong>Precise</strong> motion accuracy. <strong>Sharp</strong> imaging and <strong>smooth</strong> motion transition are all features which have elevated the <strong>HTC Vive</strong> as the <strong>no.1 VR Headset</strong> in the <strong>VR</strong> market.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_image admin_label="Image" src="http://localhost/ITico/web/viarama.co.uk/public_html/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/CV1_HMD_Back16Feb1.png" show_in_lightbox="off" url_new_window="off" use_overlay="off" animation="left" sticky="off" align="left" force_fullwidth="off" always_center_on_mobile="on"] [/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label="row" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" width_unit="off" custom_width_px="1080px" custom_width_percent="80%" use_custom_gutter="off" gutter_width="3" padding_mobile="off" allow_player_pause="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="on" make_equal="off" column_padding_mobile="on" parallax_1="off" parallax_method_1="on" parallax_2="off" parallax_method_2="on" parallax_3="off" parallax_method_3="on" parallax_4="off" parallax_method_4="on"][et_pb_column type="1_4"][et_pb_image admin_label="Image" src="http://localhost/ITico/web/viarama.co.uk/public_html/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/CV1_HMD_BackPers16Feb19-1.png" show_in_lightbox="off" url_new_window="off" use_overlay="off" animation="left" sticky="off" align="left" force_fullwidth="off" always_center_on_mobile="on"] [/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_text admin_label="Text" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left"]\r\n\r\nThe <strong>HTC Vive</strong> has a 2160 x 1200 (1080 x 1200 per eye) pixel PenTile OLED display and a refresh rate of 90Hz giving a<strong> crystal clear image</strong> and<strong> smooth motion</strong> for the user and is the only <strong>VR Headset</strong> which will allow the user full control to move around within their virtual world. It’s 110 degree field of view gives <strong>exceptional</strong> lateral field of vision for any discerning user.\r\n\r\n<strong>Viarama</strong> also offers a very large physical space in which to explore the virtual world where you can walk around while interacting– known as <strong>Room Scale Virtual Reality</strong>.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_4"][et_pb_image admin_label="Image" src="http://localhost/ITico/web/viarama.co.uk/public_html/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/CV1_HMD_FrontPers16Feb19.png" show_in_lightbox="off" url_new_window="off" use_overlay="off" animation="left" sticky="off" align="left" force_fullwidth="off" always_center_on_mobile="on"] [/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label="row" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" width_unit="off" custom_width_px="1080px" custom_width_percent="80%" use_custom_gutter="off" gutter_width="3" padding_mobile="off" allow_player_pause="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="on" make_equal="off" column_padding_mobile="on" parallax_1="off" parallax_method_1="on" parallax_2="off" parallax_method_2="on" parallax_3="off" parallax_method_3="on" parallax_4="off" parallax_method_4="on"][et_pb_column type="4_4"][et_pb_cta admin_label="Call To Action" title="The future has arrived... What will you be part of?" button_url="http://google.com" url_new_window="off" button_text="BOOK YOUR VIRTUAL REALITY SESSION NOW" use_background_color="on" background_color="#141414" background_layout="dark" text_orientation="center" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_width="1px" border_style="solid" custom_button=