roduction begins…</h4>\r\n<h4><strong>Virtual Reality</strong> is only emerging and this is your chance to get in at the <strong>cutting edge</strong> and be one of the first to <strong>experience the future</strong>.</h4>\r\n[/et_pb_slide][et_pb_slide button_link="#" background_image="http://localhost/ITico/web/viarama.co.uk/public_html/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/VivePort_4000x1700_Stonehenge_Man.jpg" background_position="center" background_size="contain" background_color="#020202" use_bg_overlay="on" bg_overlay_color="rgba(5,5,5,0.56)" use_text_overlay="off" alignment="center" background_layout="dark" allow_player_pause="off" text_border_radius="3" disabled="off" header_font_select="default" header_font="||||" body_font_select="default" body_font="||||" custom_button="off" button_font_select="default" button_font="||||" button_use_icon="default" button_icon_placement="right" button_on_hover="on"]\r\n<h4><strong>Experience</strong> a world lost in time when the <strong>dinosaurs</strong> roamed the earth…</h4>\r\n<h4>Walk along the top of the world’s <strong>highest</strong> mountain…</h4>\r\n<h4><strong>Travel</strong> through space and <strong>discover</strong> the planets…</h4>\r\n<h4><strong>Face your fears</strong> whatever they may be…..</h4>\r\n<h4>Rides too <strong>dangerous</strong> to build, <strong>nightmares</strong> too scary to speak of…</h4>\r\n<h4><strong>Travel</strong> round the body via the veins to <strong>experience</strong> science first hand…</h4>\r\n<h4><strong>Discover</strong> life as a<strong> fast</strong> jet pilot from the Captain’s seat…</h4>\r\n<h4><strong>Become</strong> a celebrity and <strong>indulge</strong> with private screenings in your own home cinema…</h4>\r\n<h4><strong>Explore</strong> lost worlds undersea...</h4>\r\n<h4><strong>Fight</strong> off hordes of zombies or stormtroopers on Tatooine ...</h4>\r\n<h4><strong>Viarama</strong> is beyond your <strong>imagination</strong>.</h4>\r\n[/et_pb_slide] [/et_pb_slider][et_pb_